== 防灾措施 ==
面对飓风来袭，[[美国国家气象局|美国国家气象局]]驻[[新奥尔良|新奥尔良]]办事处于8月23日开始发布[[热带气旋警告|热带气旋警告]]和公告。首先是新奥尔良至德克萨斯州[[马塔哥达县|马塔哥达县]][[马塔哥达_(德克萨斯州)|马塔哥达]]（{{lang|en|Matagorda}}）之间的[[美国墨西哥湾沿岸地区|美国墨西哥湾沿岸地区]]于{{lang|en|UTC}}当天凌晨4点30分收到风暴警告，称有相当强烈的天气系统逐渐逼近。次日气旋出人意料地转向北上，上述风暴警告的生效范围东移至路易斯安那州[[摩根城_(路易斯安那州)|摩根城]]至德克萨斯州[[加尔维斯敦_(德克萨斯州)|加尔维斯敦]]；摩根城至阿拉巴马州[[莫比尔_(阿拉巴马州)|莫比尔]]之间的气象部门则于{{lang|en|UTC}}凌晨4点发布飓风警告。莫比尔向东直至[[佛罗里达州|佛罗里达州]][[阿巴拉契科拉_(佛罗里达州)|阿巴拉契科拉]]也收到风暴警告。飓风在陆地上空迅速减弱后，新奥尔良办事处于{{lang|en|UTC}}8月25日早上5点中止发布警告和公告。为了把信息送抵可能受到影响的地区，气象部门采用包括信件、电报在内的多种方式传送警告。<ref name="New Orleans District">{{cite journal | title = New Orleans Forecast District | journal = Monthly Weather Review | date = 1926-08-01 | volume = 54 | issue = 8 | pages = 357–358 | doi = 10.1175/1520-0493(1926)54<357b:NOFD>2.0.CO;2 | accessdate = 2016-12-31 | bibcode = 1926MWRv...54R.357. | url = https://docs.lib.noaa.gov/rescue/mwr/054/mwr-054-08-0357b.pdf | archivedate = 2016-03-04 | format = PDF | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160304070939/http://docs.lib.noaa.gov/rescue/mwr/054/mwr-054-08-0357b.pdf | deadurl = no }}</ref>气旋逼近海岸期间，美国国家气象局还开始尝试通过无线电向海上船只发送[[地面天气分析图|地面天气分析图]]<ref name="Radio Ships">{{cite news | last = Thomas L. | first = Stokes | title = Weather Maps to be Sent to Ships at Sea by Radio | url = https://news.google.com/newspapers?id=05sLAAAAIBAJ&sjid=lVQDAAAAIBAJ&pg=1615,1466770&dq=hurricane&hl=en | accessdate = 2016-12-31 | newspaper = The Evening Independent | date = 1926-08-24 | agency = United News | location = Washington, D.C.}}</ref>，建议莫比尔近海船只返回[[莫比尔港|莫比尔港]]（{{lang|en|Port of Mobile}}），浮动[[船坞|船坞]]及其装载的资产则转移到新奥尔良<ref name="Trains">{{cite news | title = Trains Are Delayed As Wind Rages | agency = Associated Press | url = https://news.google.com/newspapers?id=HBBPAAAAIBAJ&sjid=oUwDAAAAIBAJ&pg=5946,3218590&dq=hurricane&hl=en | accessdate = 2016-12-31 | newspaper = St. Petersburg Times | date = 2013-08-25 | location = New Orleans, Louisiana | page = 1}}</ref>。由于飓风可能会对[[棉花|棉]]业产生影响，棉花[[股票市场|股票市场]]的首比交易[[贸易利得|增益]]达到8至15个百分点<ref name="Goes North">{{cite news | title = Tropical Storm Goes Northward | accessdate = 2016-12-31 | newspaper = The Evening Independent | location = New Orleans, Louisiana | pages = 1, 7 | url = https://news.google.com/newspapers?id=1JsLAAAAIBAJ&sjid=lVQDAAAAIBAJ&pg=2850,1579819&dq=hurricane&hl=en | date = 1926-08-25}}</ref>，收盘股价净收益则高达24%<ref name="Cotton Up">{{cite news | title = Cotton Moves Up on Weather News | accessdate = 2016-12-31 | date = 1926-08-26 | newspaper = [[纽约时报|The New York Times]] | url = http://query.nytimes.com/gst/abstract.html?res=9D06E0DC163CEE3ABC4E51DFBE66838D639EDE&legacy=true | publisher = The New York Times Company}}</ref>。

== 影响 ==
[[File:Hurricane_Three_1926_Rainfall_Totals.png|thumb]]

路易斯安那州[[泰勒博恩堂区_(路易斯安那州)|泰勒博恩堂区]]测得4.6米的[[风暴潮|风暴潮]]，坦巴利耶湾（{{lang|en|Timbalier Bay}}）的潮水比正常水平高三米。[[新运河灯塔|新运河灯塔]]受到狂风大浪破坏，这座灯塔此前已因[[1915年新奥尔良飓风|1915年新奥尔良飓风]]受损，此次再度受创后，有关部门将灯塔地基加高0.9米。坦巴利耶湾的第三号灯塔也受到气旋破坏。<ref name="LA Hurricanes" />风暴期间，多艘未能及时撤回港口的小型[[双桅纵帆船|双桅]]渔船失踪<ref name="Nevada">{{cite news | title = A Tropical Storm Hits Gulf | newspaper = Nevada Daily Mail | date = 1926-08-26 | accessdate = 2016-12-31 | url = https://news.google.com/newspapers?id=TlMrAAAAIBAJ&sjid=-dcEAAAAIBAJ&pg=1814,6019340&dq=hurricane&hl=en | page = 1 | location = New Orleans, Louisiana Coast}}</ref>。[[密西西比河|密西西比河]]上流位于[[唐纳森维尔_(路易斯安那州)|唐纳森维尔]]附近流域有一艘船沉没<ref name="LA Hurricanes">{{cite book | title = Louisiana Hurricane History | url = http://www.wpc.ncep.noaa.gov/research/lahur.pdf | format = PDF | publisher = [[美国国家气象局|United States National Oceanic and Atmospheric Administration's National Weather Service]] | accessdate = 2016-12-31 | last1 = Roth | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20161221212736/http://www.wpc.ncep.noaa.gov/research/lahur.pdf | first1 = David M | author2 = Hydrometeorological Prediction Center | pages = 31–32 | archivedate = 2016-12-21 | deadurl = no }}</ref>。

风暴登陆时，路易斯安那州海岸沿线风力达到飓风强度。[[格兰德艾尔_(路易斯安那州)|格兰德艾尔]]测得每小时160公里的持续风速，[[蒂博_(路易斯安那州)|蒂博]]和[[拿破仑维尔_(路易斯安那州)|拿破仑维尔]]的阵风时速估计高达195公里。<ref name="LA Hurricanes" />蒂博有三所[[教堂|教堂]]、一间仓库和十家商店被毁。新奥尔良的一间气象站测得全市最高的时速84公里阵风。新奥尔良至巴吞鲁日间地区受到重创，许多树木连根拔起，多个谷仓倒塌，新奥尔良部分窗户因狂风破损。<ref name="Dark">{{cite news | title = City In Darkness | url = https://news.google.com/newspapers?id=0DJFAAAAIBAJ&sjid=j7sMAAAAIBAJ&pg=3112,6712885&dq=hurricane&hl=en | accessdate = 2016-12-31 | newspaper = The Telegraph-Herald | date = 1926-08-26 | pages = 1}}</ref>巴吞鲁日出现停电，当地电力公司因此蒙受约两万美元的损失<ref name="LA Hurricanes" />。摩根城的通讯线缆中断，导致该市同外界失去联系，还有许多房屋的屋顶被狂风刮落<ref name="Trains" />。摩根角（{{lang|en|Morgan Point}}）近海有一艘[[渡船|渡船]]失事<ref name="Dark" />。霍玛在风暴来袭期间估计有90%的甘蔗毁于一旦，市内的[[糖仓|糖仓]]和一座[[美国圣公会|圣公会教堂]]也被摧毁<ref name="LA Hurricanes" />。由于风力太大，对铁路运输构成威胁，[[南太平洋铁路|南太平洋铁路]]的三辆[[铁路列车|列车]]一度困在[[杰佛逊堂区_(路易斯安那州)|杰佛逊堂区]]的[[埃文代尔_(路易斯安那州)|埃文代尔]]（{{lang|en|Avondale}}）<ref name="Trains" />。狂风暴雨还引起一架[[邮政飞机|邮政飞机]]坠毁<ref name="Path Sweep" />。[[杜兰大学|杜兰大学]]因气旋来袭发生火灾，将化学系的一幢楼房烧毁<ref name="Path Sweep">{{cite news | title = Southern States In Path of Storm; Sweeps Louisiana | url = http://pqasb.pqarchiver.com/ajc_historic/doc/499704705.html?FMT=CITE&FMTS=CITE:AI&type=historic&date=Aug%2026,%201926&author=&pub=The%20Atlanta%20Constitution&edition=&startpage=&desc=Southern%20States%20In%20Path%20of%20Storm;%20Sweeps%20Louisiana | accessdate = 2016-12-31 | newspaper = Atlanta Constitution | date = 1926-08-26 | location = Atlanta, Georgia | archive-date = 2017-05-11 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20170511091523/http://pqasb.pqarchiver.com/ajc_historic/doc/499704705.html?FMT=CITE&FMTS=CITE:AI&type=historic&date=Aug%2026,%201926&author=&pub=The%20Atlanta%20Constitution&edition=&startpage=&desc=Southern%20States%20In%20Path%20of%20Storm;%20Sweeps%20Louisiana | dead-url = no }}</ref>，新奥尔良另有多地发生火灾<ref name="Trains" />。

飓风登陆前，美国墨西哥湾沿岸地区的大气变得很不稳定，这种因素同来袭的风暴共同影响，在沿海地区降下暴雨，其中唐纳森维尔降雨量最高，8月25至26日的短短24小时里就降下370毫米<ref name="rainfall">{{cite web | title = Rainfall Associated With Hurricanes (And Other Tropical Disturbances) | last2 = Molansky | first2 = S. | pages = 32–33 | url = http://www.wpc.ncep.noaa.gov/tropical/rain/1956NHRPreportNo3.pdf | publisher = United States Weather Bureau's National Hurricane Research Project | accessdate = 2016-12-31 | last1 = Schoner | first1 = R.W. | archivedate = 2016-03-04 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160304065316/http://www.wpc.ncep.noaa.gov/tropical/rain/1956NHRPreportNo3.pdf | deadurl = no | format = PDF }}</ref>。包括唐纳森维尔在内的11个地点24小时降雨量创下历史新高。泰勒博恩堂区的[[施里弗_(路易斯安那州)|施里弗]]（{{lang|en|Schriever}}）有座[[长山核桃|长山核桃]][[果园|果园]]在暴雨中被毁，[[克罗利_(路易斯安那州)|克罗利]]的庄稼受损。<ref name="LA Hurricanes" />其他沿海地区的降雨量大多在76毫米以上。佛罗里达州西北狭长地带的最高降雨量有250毫米，局部降雨量至少也有130毫米。<ref name="rainfall" />整场风暴共造成25人丧生，损失总额估计为600万美元，其中400万美元属[[基础设施|基础设施]]受损<ref name="Severe">{{cite journal | title = Severe Local Hail and Wind Storms, August, 1926 | journal = Monthly Weather Review | date = 1926-08-01 | volume = 54 | issue = 8 | pages = 354–355 | doi = 10.1175/1520-0493(1926)54<354:SLHAWS>2.0.CO;2 | bibcode = 1926MWRv...54..354. | url = https://docs.lib.noaa.gov/rescue/mwr/054/mwr-054-08-0354.pdf | accessdate = 2016-12-31 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160304111237/http://docs.lib.noaa.gov/rescue/mwr/054/mwr-054-08-0354.pdf | deadurl = no | archivedate = 2016-03-04 | format = PDF }}</ref><ref name="LA Hurricanes" />。风暴过去后，[[美国红十字会|美国红十字会]]向霍玛及其他灾区提供援助物资并协助善后工作<ref name="25 Perish">{{cite news | title = 25 Perish in Hurricane | url = http://query.nytimes.com/gst/abstract.html?res=9C0DE5D81E3AEE3ABC4151DFBE66838D639EDE&legacy=true | accessdate = 2016-12-31 | newspaper = The New York Times | date = 1926-08-29 | publisher = The New York Times Company | archive-date = 2018-01-05 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20180105070257/http://query.nytimes.com/gst/abstract.html?res=9C0DE5D81E3AEE3ABC4151DFBE66838D639EDE&legacy=true | dead-url = no }}</ref><ref name="RC">{{cite news | title = Red Cross to Help | date = 1926-08-29 | agency = Associated Press | location = Washington, D.C. | page = 1,7 | url = https://news.google.com/newspapers?id=HxBPAAAAIBAJ&sjid=oUwDAAAAIBAJ&pg=6309,4157278&dq=hurricane&hl=en | accessdate = 2016-12-31 | newspaper = St. Petersburg Times}}</ref>。
